      "text": "第一回！　franさんの漫画会議～！\n今回から、遙子さんも参加してくれますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first fran-san’s manga meeting～！\nHaruko-san will be joining us from today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.3711341857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "は～い！　franさんの企画をお手伝いに来た\n佐伯遙子、十七歳ですっ。イラストなら任せてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi~! Haruko Saeki‚ 17 years old‚ here to help\nwith your project! Leave the illustrations to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0378008524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "優は残念ながら予定が重なっていて、参加出来ないそう\nですが、これから三人で頑張っていきますわよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unfortunately‚ Yu has a scheduling conflict and won’t be able to join us.\nBut let’s do our best‚ the three of us~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5000001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.0429254531
    },
    {
