      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、漫画家の先生が見つからなくて自分で描くことに\nなったけど……アシスタントがこの二人で大丈夫かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I couldn’t find a manga artist‚ so I decided to draw it myself…\nbut I wonder if things will work out with these two as my assistants?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.5335151671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
