      "text": "さっき絵を見せたけど、主要なキャラはあんな感じの\nタッチで、よほどのことがない限り私が描くつもりよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I showed you the drawing earlier‚ but the main characters will be in that style.\nUnless something comes up‚ I plan on drawing them myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333336512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
