      "text": "手伝ってくれるっていうなら、すずは背景担当、遙子は\nベタ塗りやトーン、あとはモブキャラを描いてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re willing to help‚ Suzu‚ you’ll be in charge of the backgrounds‚ and Haruko‚\nyou can handle the inking‚ tones‚ and drawing the minor characters‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3333354313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
